name: Listened to Malik Rosier on life after football + John Ruiz’s launch party

content.html:
Manny returns from his trip to Phoenix and a launch party for Miami booster John Ruiz’s new boat racing series with some tidbits of info. Former Hurricanes quarterback Malik Rosier, who led Miami to its only ACC title game appearance, joins Manny to discuss life after football as a private QB coach for Tyler Van Dyke and Jacurri Brown, dealing with evolving defenses as a second-year starter, the pressures of social media and more.
